                              without marriage and intercourse ...” (last strophe of the hymn <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4274AkkonuB">ʾAkko-nu bǝʾsi</title>)</title>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.3">
                           <locus target="#5vb">5vb</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5775PraisetoMary">Sǝbḥāt laki Māryām ba-ḫʷǝlqʷa malāʾǝkt za-ʾaryām ... “Glory to you,
