                           <locus from="5vb" to="6ra">5vb-6ra</locus>
                           <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3093RepCh373">ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝya Māryām ʾǝmmu la-ʾIyasus kahāli ... “O my Lady Mary,
