                  <handDesc>
                     
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Mediocre but careful</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red</seg>
                        <date>19th century</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሰ፡ or ሰላ፡ ለ፡</abbr> for <expan>ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ </expan> (<locus target="#5rb">5rb</locus>)</item>
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ሰብ፡</abbr> for <expan>ሰብሐት፡</expan> (<locus target="#5vb">5vb</locus>)</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the donors; groups of lines in
                           the incipit page of Text I-1; incipit of (sub)sections and partly section
                           numbers of Text I-4; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text
                           dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">Readings are indicated by the names of the feasts,
                              written in the upper margin in two different hands (partly in red):
                              ዘልደታ፡ አመ፬፡ ለግንቦት: <locus target="#49va">fol. 49va</locus> አመ፫፡ ለታኅሣሥ፡
                              በዓታ: <locus target="#51rb">fol. 51rb</locus> አመ፳ወ፪፡ ለታኅሣሥ፡ በዘዜነዋ:
                                 <locus target="#53rb">fol. 53rb</locus> ዘልደተ፡ ክርስቶስ: <locus target="#54vb">fol. 54vb</locus> አመ፳ወ፩፡ ለጥር: <locus target="#56ra">fol. 56ra</locus> ዘደብረ፡ ምጥማቅ: <locus target="#57vb">fol.
                                 57vb</locus> ዘዕሁድ: <locus target="#64vb">fol. 64vb</locus> ዘጽዮን:
                              አመ፳ወ፩፡ ለኅዳር: <locus target="#70rb">fol. 70rb</locus> ዘበዓለ፡ ፍልሰታ፡
                              አመ፲ወ፮፡ ለነሐሴ: <locus target="#74ra">fol. 74ra</locus> ዘኪዳነ፡ ምሕረት:
                                 <locus target="#78rb">fol. 78rb</locus> ዘትንሣኤ: <locus target="#79vb">fol. 79vb</locus> አመ፡ ፰፡ ለሰኔ፡ በአንቅዓ፡ ወልደ፡ ወዘጥምቀት:
                                 <locus target="#88ra">fol. 88ra</locus> አመ፲ወ፪፡ ለታኅሣሥ: <locus target="#109va">fol. 109va</locus> በበዓለ፡ ቍስቋም: <locus target="#111vb">fol. 111vb</locus> ዘቅዳሴ፡ ቤታ፡ አመ፳ወ፩፡ለሰኔ፡: <locus target="#113rb">fol. 113rb</locus>
                           </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc>The title ተአምረ፡ ማርያም is written on fol. 1, in pen. </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>Omitted letters, words or passages are written interlineally: e.g., fols. 8va, 16vb, 23va, 33vb, 48vb, 75rb, 87vb. 94va, 114va. </desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e4">
                           <desc> Spaces for rubricated names of the donor(s) are left unfilled: fols. 81ra-83vb, 87rb, 90vb-117ra.</desc>
                        </item>
